{
  "video_id": "u1_dYypojbE",
  "title": "The best way to help is often just to listen | Sophie Andrews",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12921.0,
      "end_time": 15325.0,
      "text": "After cutting her arm with a broken glass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15349.0,
      "end_time": 20423.0,
      "text": "she fell into a fitful, exhausted sleep on the railway station platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21649.0,
      "end_time": 24443.0,
      "text": "Early in the morning, when the station toilets were opened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24467.0,
      "end_time": 27640.0,
      "text": "she got painfully to her feet, and made her way over to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28458.0,
      "end_time": 30537.0,
      "text": "When she saw her reflection in the mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30561.0,
      "end_time": 31828.0,
      "text": "she started to cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32792.0,
      "end_time": 34974.0,
      "text": "Her face was dirty and tearstained;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34998.0,
      "end_time": 37323.0,
      "text": "her shirt was ripped and covered in blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38380.0,
      "end_time": 42840.0,
      "text": "She looked as if she&#39;d been on the streets for three months, not three days."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42998.0,
      "end_time": 45449.0,
      "text": "She washed herself as best she could."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45473.0,
      "end_time": 48140.0,
      "text": "Her arms and stomach were hurting badly."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49149.0,
      "end_time": 50728.0,
      "text": "She tried to clean the wounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50752.0,
      "end_time": 53934.0,
      "text": "but any pressure she applied just started the bleeding again."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55244.0,
      "end_time": 59800.0,
      "text": "She needed stitches, but there was no way she would go to a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59718.0,
      "end_time": 61567.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d have sent her back home again."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61591.0,
      "end_time": 62741.0,
      "text": "Back to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63964.0,
      "end_time": 65893.0,
      "text": "She tightened her jacket --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65917.0,
      "end_time": 68450.0,
      "text": "well, fastened her jacket tightly to cover the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69109.0,
      "end_time": 71442.0,
      "text": "She looked back at herself in the mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71466.0,
      "end_time": 74643.0,
      "text": "She looked a little better than before but was past caring."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78736.0,
      "text": "There was only one thing she could think of doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79930.0,
      "end_time": 82433.0,
      "text": "She came out of the station and into a phone box nearby."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83456.0,
      "end_time": 87370.0,
      "text": "(Telephone rings)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88863.0,
      "end_time": 91607.0,
      "text": "(Telephone rings)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92339.0,
      "end_time": 94300.0,
      "text": "Woman: Samaritans, can I help you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97133.0,
      "end_time": 99651.0,
      "text": "Hello, Samaritans. Can I help you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100760.0,
      "end_time": 101726.0,
      "text": "Girl: (Crying) I -- I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102895.0,
      "end_time": 106530.0,
      "text": "Woman: What&#39;s happened? You sound very upset."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106770.0,
      "end_time": 108378.0,
      "text": "(Girl cries)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110799.0,
      "end_time": 112720.0,
      "text": "Woman: Why not start with your name?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112744.0,
      "end_time": 114677.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Pam. What can I call you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117894.0,
      "end_time": 120220.0,
      "text": "Where are you speaking from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 120460.0,
      "end_time": 121196.0,
      "text": "Are you safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122244.0,
      "end_time": 124264.0,
      "text": "Girl: It&#39;s a phone box in London."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125609.0,
      "end_time": 128588.0,
      "text": "Pam: You sound very young. How old are you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128612.0,
      "end_time": 129762.0,
      "text": "Girl: Fourteen."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130374.0,
      "end_time": 132739.0,
      "text": "Pam: And what&#39;s happened to make you so upset?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133128.0,
      "end_time": 137220.0,
      "text": "Girl: I just want to die. Every day I wake up and wish I was dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137460.0,
      "end_time": 140767.0,
      "text": "If he doesn&#39;t kill me, then, I think, I want to do it myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141949.0,
      "end_time": 143616.0,
      "text": "Pam: I&#39;m glad you called."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 144165.0,
      "end_time": 146310.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start at the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 148854.0,
      "end_time": 152140.0,
      "text": "Sophie Andrews: Pam continued to gently ask the girl about herself."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152380.0,
      "end_time": 154582.0,
      "text": "She didn&#39;t say much; there were lots of silences."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 155222.0,
      "end_time": 156576.0,
      "text": "But she knew she was there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156600.0,
      "end_time": 159952.0,
      "text": "and having Pam on the end of the phone felt so comforting."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 162365.0,
      "end_time": 164793.0,
      "text": "The 14-year-old that made that call was me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166189.0,
      "end_time": 168122.0,
      "text": "That was me in the phone box."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168451.0,
      "end_time": 172335.0,
      "text": "I was running away from home, sleeping rough on the streets in London."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173426.0,
      "end_time": 176458.0,
      "text": "I was being sexually abused by my father and his friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177681.0,
      "end_time": 180747.0,
      "text": "I was self-harming every day. I was suicidal."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 183847.0,
      "end_time": 187502.0,
      "text": "The first time I called Samaritans, I was 12 and absolutely desperate."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 188371.0,
      "end_time": 191270.0,
      "text": "It was a few months after my mother had deserted me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191510.0,
      "end_time": 193251.0,
      "text": "walked out and left me in the family home."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 194770.0,
      "end_time": 197482.0,
      "text": "And the abuse I was suffering at the hands of my father and his friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 197506.0,
      "end_time": 199239.0,
      "text": "had left me a total wreck."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200232.0,
      "end_time": 202839.0,
      "text": "I was running away, I was missing school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 202863.0,
      "end_time": 204196.0,
      "text": "I was arriving drunk."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204957.0,
      "end_time": 207424.0,
      "text": "I was without hope and wanted to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 208934.0,
      "end_time": 210851.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where Samaritans came in."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 213460.0,
      "end_time": 216345.0,
      "text": "Samaritans has been around since 1953."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 216878.0,
      "end_time": 220497.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a 24/7 confidential helpline in the UK"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 220521.0,
      "end_time": 223543.0,
      "text": "for anyone who might be feeling desperate or suicidal."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 224360.0,
      "end_time": 225503.0,
      "text": "Which I certainly was."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226411.0,
      "end_time": 229592.0,
      "text": "Volunteers answer the phone around the clock every day of the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229616.0,
      "end_time": 231148.0,
      "text": "and calls are confidential."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 233204.0,
      "end_time": 235744.0,
      "text": "During my teenage years, when I was most desperate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 235768.0,
      "end_time": 237901.0,
      "text": "Samaritans became my lifeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238776.0,
      "end_time": 241426.0,
      "text": "They promised me total confidentiality."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241450.0,
      "end_time": 243259.0,
      "text": "And that allowed me to trust them."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244315.0,
      "end_time": 247506.0,
      "text": "Disturbing as they no doubt found my story, they never showed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248457.0,
      "end_time": 251529.0,
      "text": "They were always there for me and listened without judgment."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 252244.0,
      "end_time": 254426.0,
      "text": "Mostly, they gently encouraged me to get help;"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 254450.0,
      "end_time": 256397.0,
      "text": "I never felt out of control with them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257140.0,
      "end_time": 258188.0,
      "text": "an interesting parallel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 258212.0,
      "end_time": 261774.0,
      "text": "as I felt so out of control in every other aspect of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 262632.0,
      "end_time": 264841.0,
      "text": "It felt my self-harm was probably the only area"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264865.0,
      "end_time": 266710.0,
      "text": "where I felt I had any control."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 269442.0,
      "end_time": 273175.0,
      "text": "A few years later, I managed to get some control in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 273641.0,
      "end_time": 275903.0,
      "text": "And I had appropriate support around me"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275927.0,
      "end_time": 278450.0,
      "text": "to allow me to live with what had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278387.0,
      "end_time": 281144.0,
      "text": "I had become a survivor of abuse rather than a victim."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 282204.0,
      "end_time": 284688.0,
      "text": "And at 21, I contacted Samaritans again."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285299.0,
      "end_time": 288370.0,
      "text": "This time because I wanted to become a volunteer."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288426.0,
      "end_time": 289878.0,
      "text": "Wanted to pay something back"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 289903.0,
      "end_time": 292789.0,
      "text": "to the organization that had really saved my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 294674.0,
      "end_time": 298323.0,
      "text": "I knew that the simple act of listening in an empathetic way"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 298348.0,
      "end_time": 300460.0,
      "text": "could have a profound effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300991.0,
      "end_time": 304220.0,
      "text": "I knew that somebody listening to me without judgment"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304470.0,
      "end_time": 305737.0,
      "text": "would make the biggest difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 307673.0,
      "end_time": 310648.0,
      "text": "So I caught up with my education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310672.0,
      "end_time": 314617.0,
      "text": "found someone I could persuade to give me a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314641.0,
      "end_time": 317394.0,
      "text": "and I enjoyed my volunteering at Samaritans."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317744.0,
      "end_time": 320237.0,
      "text": "And when I say \"enjoyed,\" it&#39;s an odd word to use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320261.0,
      "end_time": 322324.0,
      "text": "because no one would want to think of anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 322348.0,
      "end_time": 324403.0,
      "text": "being in absolute distress or pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 325530.0,
      "end_time": 327776.0,
      "text": "But I knew that that profound impact of that listening ear"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 327800.0,
      "end_time": 331370.0,
      "text": "and someone being alongside me at that desperate time"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331610.0,
      "end_time": 332275.0,
      "text": "had the biggest impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 332300.0,
      "end_time": 334895.0,
      "text": "and I felt a great sense of fulfillment"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334919.0,
      "end_time": 337181.0,
      "text": "that I was able to help people as a Samaritan."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 338450.0,
      "end_time": 342347.0,
      "text": "In my years volunteering at Samaritans, I was asked to perform many roles."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342371.0,
      "end_time": 345537.0,
      "text": "But I guess the peak came in 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 345561.0,
      "end_time": 348371.0,
      "text": "when I was asked to chair the organization for three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 348395.0,
      "end_time": 350744.0,
      "text": "So I had actually gone from that vulnerable caller"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 350768.0,
      "end_time": 352768.0,
      "text": "in the phone box, desperate for help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 352792.0,
      "end_time": 355290.0,
      "text": "to being the national lead for the organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 355530.0,
      "end_time": 357586.0,
      "text": "and responsible for 22,000 volunteers."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 359180.0,
      "end_time": 360748.0,
      "text": "I actually used to joke at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 360772.0,
      "end_time": 362897.0,
      "text": "and say if you really screwed up as a caller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 362922.0,
      "end_time": 364589.0,
      "text": "you might end up running the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364613.0,
      "end_time": 365764.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 365788.0,
      "end_time": 366958.0,
      "text": "Which I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366982.0,
      "end_time": 372690.0,
      "text": "But I guess in a world which is dominated by professionalizing everything we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 372930.0,
      "end_time": 374585.0,
      "text": "I really understood that that simple act of listening"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 374609.0,
      "end_time": 376744.0,
      "text": "could have such a life-changing effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 377578.0,
      "end_time": 379600.0,
      "text": "I guess it&#39;s a simple concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 379310.0,
      "end_time": 381474.0,
      "text": "that can be applied across all areas of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 382768.0,
      "end_time": 384799.0,
      "text": "So in the 1980s, when I called Samaritans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 384824.0,
      "end_time": 387394.0,
      "text": "child abuse was a subject no one wanted to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388220.0,
      "end_time": 391873.0,
      "text": "Victims were often blamed, victims were often judged."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 393236.0,
      "end_time": 397510.0,
      "text": "And it was a topic of shame, and no one really wanted to talk about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398284.0,
      "end_time": 401847.0,
      "text": "Today, judgment and shame surround a different issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 401871.0,
      "end_time": 404275.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a different stigma that&#39;s out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 404633.0,
      "end_time": 408440.0,
      "text": "And the stigma that&#39;s there today is to talk about loneliness."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 410180.0,
      "end_time": 413522.0,
      "text": "Loneliness and isolation have profound health impacts."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 413546.0,
      "end_time": 417305.0,
      "text": "Being lonely can have a significant impact on your own well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 418220.0,
      "end_time": 420180.0,
      "text": "Recent systematic review of research"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 420204.0,
      "end_time": 422800.0,
      "text": "actually said that it increased the mortality rates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 422824.0,
      "end_time": 424149.0,
      "text": "or premature death rates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 424173.0,
      "end_time": 425506.0,
      "text": "by up to 30 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 426556.0,
      "end_time": 430573.0,
      "text": "It can lead to higher blood pressure, higher levels of depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 430597.0,
      "end_time": 432779.0,
      "text": "and actually aligned to mortality rates"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 432803.0,
      "end_time": 437148.0,
      "text": "that might be more associated with alcohol abuse or smoking cigarettes."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 437913.0,
      "end_time": 441332.0,
      "text": "Loneliness is actually more harmful that smoking 15 cigarettes."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 441667.0,
      "end_time": 442857.0,
      "text": "A day."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 443215.0,
      "end_time": 444875.0,
      "text": "Not in your life, in your day."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 445324.0,
      "end_time": 448244.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also associated with higher levels of dementia."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 448268.0,
      "end_time": 450155.0,
      "text": "So a recent study also found"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 450180.0,
      "end_time": 453961.0,
      "text": "that lonely people are twice at risk of Alzheimer&#39;s disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 455728.0,
      "end_time": 459896.0,
      "text": "Of course, there&#39;s many people that live alone who are not lonely."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 460696.0,
      "end_time": 464323.0,
      "text": "But being a caregiver for a partner that maybe has dementia"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 464347.0,
      "end_time": 466800.0,
      "text": "can be a very lonely place."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 467163.0,
      "end_time": 470291.0,
      "text": "And a recent landmark study gave us a very good, clear definition"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 470315.0,
      "end_time": 471830.0,
      "text": "of what loneliness is."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 471854.0,
      "end_time": 475256.0,
      "text": "And it said it&#39;s a subjective, unwelcome feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 475280.0,
      "end_time": 477614.0,
      "text": "of a lack or loss of companionship."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 478185.0,
      "end_time": 480249.0,
      "text": "And it happens when there&#39;s a mismatch"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 480273.0,
      "end_time": 483939.0,
      "text": "between the quality and the quantity of relationships that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 483963.0,
      "end_time": 485310.0,
      "text": "and those that we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 487700.0,
      "end_time": 489746.0,
      "text": "Now in my life, the best help I&#39;ve ever received"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 489770.0,
      "end_time": 491919.0,
      "text": "has been from those personal connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 491944.0,
      "end_time": 494475.0,
      "text": "and being listened to in an empathetic way."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 495561.0,
      "end_time": 499600.0,
      "text": "Professionals, and I&#39;m conscious I&#39;m speaking to a room of professionals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 499300.0,
      "end_time": 500426.0,
      "text": "have a very important place."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 500451.0,
      "end_time": 503466.0,
      "text": "But for me, a volunteer giving up their time"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 503490.0,
      "end_time": 507220.0,
      "text": "and listening to me without judgment in a confidential way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 507244.0,
      "end_time": 509998.0,
      "text": "had such a huge, life-changing effect for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 510546.0,
      "end_time": 513130.0,
      "text": "And that was something that really stayed with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 513561.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515935.00000000006,
      "text": "So as you will have gathered, in my teenage years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 515957.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519872.99999999994,
      "text": "I was off the rails, I was going every day wondering if I&#39;d even live the next day."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 519898.0,
      "end_time": 523808.0,
      "text": "But that profound impact of the volunteer listening to me stayed with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 524673.0,
      "end_time": 526799.0,
      "text": "When I finally got to a point in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 526823.0,
      "end_time": 529371.0,
      "text": "where I felt I could live with what had happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 529395.0,
      "end_time": 531530.0,
      "text": "I wanted to pay something back."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 531990.0,
      "end_time": 533140.0,
      "text": "And in my experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 533164.0,
      "end_time": 536540.0,
      "text": "people who have been helped in a transforming way"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 536780.0,
      "end_time": 537927.0,
      "text": "always want to pay something back."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 539450.0,
      "end_time": 543645.0,
      "text": "So I started paying back by my 25 years volunteering with Samaritans."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 545125.0,
      "end_time": 547158.0,
      "text": "And then, in 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 547182.0,
      "end_time": 550831.0,
      "text": "picking up on that whole issue and the new stigma of loneliness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 550855.0,
      "end_time": 554466.0,
      "text": "I launched a new national helpline in the UK for older people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 554490.0,
      "end_time": 555696.0,
      "text": "called The Silver Line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 555720.0,
      "end_time": 559840.0,
      "text": "which is there to support lonely and isolated older people."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 563793.0,
      "text": "In our short history, we&#39;ve taken 1.5 million calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 564276.0,
      "end_time": 568970.0,
      "text": "And I know we&#39;re having a big impact, based on the feedback we get every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 569411.0,
      "end_time": 572600.0,
      "text": "Some people might be calling up for a friendly chat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 572300.0,
      "end_time": 574514.0,
      "text": "maybe some information about local services."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 574538.0,
      "end_time": 577180.0,
      "text": "Some might be calling because they&#39;re suicidal."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 577204.0,
      "end_time": 579997.0,
      "text": "Some might be calling up because they&#39;re reporting abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 580693.0,
      "end_time": 584537.0,
      "text": "And some quite simply, as I was, may have simply just given up on life."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 586931.0,
      "end_time": 589685.0,
      "text": "I guess it&#39;s a really simple idea, setting up a helpline."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 589709.0,
      "end_time": 591417.0,
      "text": "And I look back to those early days"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 591442.0,
      "end_time": 595157.0,
      "text": "when I had the lofty title, I still have, of chief exec, but in the early days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 595181.0,
      "end_time": 596632.0,
      "text": "I was chief exec of myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 596982.0,
      "end_time": 600139.0,
      "text": "Which, I have to say, I had the best meetings ever in my career --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 600163.0,
      "end_time": 601314.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 601338.0,
      "end_time": 602623.0,
      "text": "as chief exec of myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 602648.0,
      "end_time": 606431.0,
      "text": "But things have moved on, and now in 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 606455.0,
      "end_time": 610183.0,
      "text": "we have over 200 staff listening to older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 610207.0,
      "end_time": 612740.0,
      "text": "every day of the year, 24/7."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 612673.0,
      "end_time": 616443.0,
      "text": "We also have over 3,000 volunteers making weekly friendship calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 616467.0,
      "end_time": 617806.0,
      "text": "from their own home."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 618767.0,
      "end_time": 620974.0,
      "text": "We also, for people that like the written word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 620998.0,
      "end_time": 623895.0,
      "text": "offer Silver Letters, and we write pen-pal letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 623919.0,
      "end_time": 626883.0,
      "text": "to older people who still enjoy receiving a letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 627497.0,
      "end_time": 630418.0,
      "text": "And we also have introduced something called Silver Circles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 630442.0,
      "end_time": 632706.0,
      "text": "you notice I&#39;m owning the word \"silver\" here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 632730.0,
      "end_time": 634733.0,
      "text": "put \"silver\" in front of it and it&#39;s ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 634757.0,
      "end_time": 636714.0,
      "text": "Silver Circles are group conference calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 636728.0,
      "end_time": 639610.0,
      "text": "where people actually talk about shared interests."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 639860.0,
      "end_time": 640935.0,
      "text": "My favorite group is the music group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 640959.0,
      "end_time": 643311.0,
      "text": "where people, every week, play musical instruments"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 643336.0,
      "end_time": 645132.0,
      "text": "down the phone to each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 645156.0,
      "end_time": 647387.0,
      "text": "Not always the same tune at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 647411.0,
      "end_time": 648949.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 648974.0,
      "end_time": 650374.0,
      "text": "But they do have fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 651260.0,
      "end_time": 652876.0,
      "text": "And \"fun\" is an interesting word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652900.0,
      "end_time": 656776.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve talked very much about desperation, loneliness and isolation."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 656800.0,
      "end_time": 660395.0,
      "text": "But if you came to our helpline in the UK, you would also hear laughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 660419.0,
      "end_time": 661864.0,
      "text": "Because at the Silver Line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 661888.0,
      "end_time": 665272.0,
      "text": "we do want to cherish the wonderful lives of older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 665296.0,
      "end_time": 667498.0,
      "text": "and all the experiences that they bring."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 667522.0,
      "end_time": 671101.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s an example, just a snippet of one of our calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 671974.0,
      "end_time": 674641.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Good morning, you&#39;re through to the Silver Line."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 674665.0,
      "end_time": 676197.0,
      "text": "My name&#39;s Alan, how can I help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 676221.0,
      "end_time": 677800.0,
      "text": "Woman: Hello, Alan. Good morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 677824.0,
      "end_time": 678974.0,
      "text": "Alan: Hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 678999.0,
      "end_time": 680156.0,
      "text": "Woman: (Chipper) Hello!"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 680180.0,
      "end_time": 681910.0,
      "text": "Alan: Oh, how are you this morning?"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 681934.0,
      "end_time": 683363.0,
      "text": "Woman: I&#39;m alright, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 683387.0,
      "end_time": 684782.0,
      "text": "Alan: I&#39;m pleased to hear it."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 684807.0,
      "end_time": 687505.0,
      "text": "Woman: What a wonderful thing the telephone is, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 688101.0,
      "end_time": 690204.0,
      "text": "Alan: It&#39;s a remarkable invention, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 690228.0,
      "end_time": 692306.0,
      "text": "Woman: I remember when I was a little girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 692331.0,
      "end_time": 693863.0,
      "text": "donkey&#39;s years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 693887.0,
      "end_time": 696782.0,
      "text": "if you wanted to make a phone call to somebody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 696807.0,
      "end_time": 698998.0,
      "text": "you had to go to a shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 699220.0,
      "end_time": 701474.0,
      "text": "and use the telephone of the shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 701498.0,
      "end_time": 705451.0,
      "text": "and pay the shop for using the telephone and have your phone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 705475.0,
      "end_time": 708164.0,
      "text": "So you didn&#39;t make phone calls just whenever you fancied."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 708188.0,
      "end_time": 709339.0,
      "text": "Alan: Oh, no."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 709363.0,
      "end_time": 711133.0,
      "text": "Woman: (Coughs) Oh, sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 711157.0,
      "end_time": 712426.0,
      "text": "(Coughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 712450.0,
      "end_time": 713776.0,
      "text": "Excuse me about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 713800.0,
      "end_time": 715498.0,
      "text": "You had to, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 715523.0,
      "end_time": 718748.0,
      "text": "confine your phone calls to the absolute essentials."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 719141.0,
      "end_time": 724788.0,
      "text": "And now, here I am, sitting in my own home in my dressing gown still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 724812.0,
      "end_time": 727783.0,
      "text": "and using the telephone, isn&#39;t it wonderful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 727807.0,
      "end_time": 730309.0,
      "text": "Alan: It is. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 730886.0,
      "end_time": 734283.0,
      "text": "SA: And that&#39;s not untypical of a call we might receive at our helpline."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 734307.0,
      "end_time": 736956.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s someone who really sees us as part of the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 737727.0,
      "end_time": 740212.0,
      "text": "So Silver Line, I guess, are now helping older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 740236.0,
      "end_time": 742442.0,
      "text": "in the same way that Samaritans has helped me."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 742466.0,
      "end_time": 745124.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re there 24/7, they&#39;re listening confidentially"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 745148.0,
      "end_time": 747671.0,
      "text": "and quite often not giving any advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 747695.0,
      "end_time": 751307.0,
      "text": "How often do we really ever listen without giving advice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 751331.0,
      "end_time": 752664.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually quite hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 752688.0,
      "end_time": 755697.0,
      "text": "Quite often on the phone calls, an older person would say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 755721.0,
      "end_time": 757663.0,
      "text": "\"Could you give me some advice, please?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 757687.0,
      "end_time": 760546.0,
      "text": "And 20 minutes later, they say, \"Thank you for your advice,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 760570.0,
      "end_time": 762310.0,
      "text": "and we realize we haven&#39;t given any."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 762334.0,
      "end_time": 763334.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 763359.0,
      "end_time": 765972.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve listened and listened, and we haven&#39;t interrupted."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 765996.0,
      "end_time": 768487.0,
      "text": "But to that person, maybe we have given advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 768511.0,
      "end_time": 770877.0,
      "text": "We recently conducted a survey at The Silver Line"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 770901.0,
      "end_time": 774558.0,
      "text": "to 3,000 older people, to ask them what they thought of the service."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 774582.0,
      "end_time": 776915.0,
      "text": "And one person quite simply came back and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 776940.0,
      "end_time": 779497.0,
      "text": "for the first time in her life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 779521.0,
      "end_time": 783306.0,
      "text": "she had what we would call in the sport cricket a wicketkeeper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 783331.0,
      "end_time": 786531.0,
      "text": "and what you would call in baseball, a catcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 786911.0,
      "end_time": 789308.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been here 48 hours, and I&#39;m talking American."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 789332.0,
      "end_time": 791347.0,
      "text": "They will not recognize me when I get home."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 791371.0,
      "end_time": 792895.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 792919.0,
      "end_time": 795656.0,
      "text": "But for the first time in her life, she had that catcher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 795680.0,
      "end_time": 797354.0,
      "text": "which is really, really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 797379.0,
      "end_time": 800280.0,
      "text": "And now it&#39;s come full circle, because actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 800520.0,
      "end_time": 802735.0,
      "text": "people that are calling Silver Line and needing a catcher"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 802759.0,
      "end_time": 805705.0,
      "text": "are now becoming catchers themselves by putting something back"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 805729.0,
      "end_time": 808736.0,
      "text": "and becoming volunteers and becoming part of our family."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 809641.0,
      "end_time": 813785.0,
      "text": "So I end my talk, really, where I started, talking about my own personal experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 814323.0,
      "end_time": 817704.0,
      "text": "Because when I talk about my life, I often say that I&#39;ve been lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 817728.0,
      "end_time": 819861.0,
      "text": "And people generally ask me why."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 820212.0,
      "end_time": 822649.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s because, at every stage of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 822673.0,
      "end_time": 827110.0,
      "text": "I have been lucky enough to have someone alongside me at the right time"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 827134.0,
      "end_time": 828897.0,
      "text": "who maybe has believed in me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 828921.0,
      "end_time": 830278.0,
      "text": "which in turn has helped me"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 830302.0,
      "end_time": 834124.0,
      "text": "just to believe a little bit more in myself, which has been so important."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 835940.0,
      "end_time": 837894.0,
      "text": "And everyone needs a catcher at some point in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 838895.0,
      "end_time": 840162.0,
      "text": "This is my catcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 840705.0,
      "end_time": 842140.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s Pam."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 842380.0,
      "end_time": 843622.0,
      "text": "And she answered the call to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 843646.0,
      "end_time": 847218.0,
      "text": "when I was that 14-year-old in the phone box, over 30 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 848973.0,
      "end_time": 853440.0,
      "text": "So never, ever underestimate the power of a simple human connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 854418.0,
      "end_time": 857580.0,
      "text": "Because it can be and so often is the power to save a life."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 858450.0,
      "end_time": 859195.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 859260.0,
      "end_time": 862412.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}